race.comment: The $160,000 Listed Bribie Handicap. THE BLACK CLOUD (12) just ran into one better at Group 3 level last time out and will have come on with that run now in the locker. Looks very well placed in this contest and should get the run of the race from gate four. Rates the testing material. GOLDEN BOOM (1) goes well for Maloney who has five wins and four placings from just 11 rides. Has a handy first-up record and can run a big race while fresh. WAY TO THE STARS (3) has been plying his trade in harder races down south before the spell and has only missed a drum once in seven first-up attempts. Has to be included. METALART (5) best of the rest from the inside marble.
